  "formulaSource": "Quarterly Payment = max(0, (Total Tax − Withheld − Paid) / (4 − Quarters Paid)). SE Tax = SE Income × 0.9235 × 15.3%. Federal tax via 2025 progressive brackets. Safe harbor = 90% of current year / 4. Per IRS Form 1040-ES, Pub 505.",
